{% section "Artifacts by Repo" %}
<!-- Auto-filled by session_manifest.py. Shows commits and uncommitted changes per repo. -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Session",
  date AS "Date",
  plan AS "Plan"
FROM "00-SHARED/Dashboards/session-manifests"
WHERE type = "session-manifest" AND date = this.date
SORT ts DESC
LIMIT 5
```
